[size=140][u]Notification Filter[/u][/size]

This mod introduces filtering functionality for some type of Notifications shown in the Ticker window and Logbook.

[size=130][u]Features[/u][/size]
[list]
[*] Set minimum changes of [b]Relation[/b] to be displayed in [b]Notification Ticker[/b] and [b]Logbook[/b] (Separately).
[*] Set a minimum amount of [b]Money[/b] transaction to be displayed in [b]Notification Ticker[/b].
[/list]
[size=130][u]Requirements[/u][/size]
[list]
[*] [b]X4: Foundations[/b]: Version 8.00HF3 or newer.
[*] [b]Mod Support APIs[/b]: Version 1.95 or higher by [url=https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/sirnukes?gameId=2659]SirNukes[/url].
[list]
[*] Available on Steam: [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2042901274]SirNukes Mod Support APIs[/url]
[*] Available on Nexus Mods: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/x4foundations/mods/503]Mod Support APIs[/url]
[/list]
[/list]
