[size=130][u]Usage[/u][/size]

After installation, please open the [b]Extension Option[/b] menu.

[spoiler][img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chemodun/X4-NotificationFilter/refs/heads/main/docs/images/extension_options.png[/img][/spoiler]

[spoiler][img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chemodun/X4-NotificationFilter/refs/heads/main/docs/images/notification_filter.png[/img][/spoiler]

[size=125][u]Relation Minimum Changes[/u][/size]

There are two different [b]Dropdowns[/b] to define the minimum change of [b]Relation[/b] to be displayed in [b]Notification ticker[/b] or recorder into [b]Logbook[/b]:
[list]
[*] [b]0 - pass all changes[/b]: Equal to the [b]vanilla[/b] game.
[*] [b]1 point or more[/b]: Only changes of [b]Relation[/b] equal or higher than 1 point will be visible.
[*] [b]2 points or more[/b]: Only changes of [b]Relation[/b] equal or higher than 2 points will be visible.
[*] [b]5 points or more[/b]: Only changes of [b]Relation[/b] equal or higher than 5 points will be visible.
[*] [b]10 points or more[/b]: Only changes of [b]Relation[/b] equal or higher than 10 points will be visible.
[/list]
[spoiler][img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chemodun/X4-NotificationFilter/refs/heads/main/docs/images/notification_filter_relation_dropdown.png[/img][/spoiler]

[size=125][u]Money Minimum Changes[/u][/size]

There is a [b]Slider[/b] to define the minimum amount of [b]Money[/b] transaction to be displayed in [b]Notification ticker[/b].

Acceptable values are between [b]0[/b] and [b]100,000,000[/b] credits with [b]1000[/b] credits step.
Zero value means that all transactions will be visible as in the [b]vanilla[/b] game.

[size=125][u]Other[/u][/size]

There is also a [b]Debug[/b] checkbox to enable debug messages for the notifications that are being processed by the filter.

